data.description: Nestled on the East edge of Wiggins is this incredible value! *No HOA* 5 bedroom, 3 bathroom ranch style home with a finished basement and fenced backyard.  Excellent living room space with specific dining area, a gas fireplace, and sliding door that leads out to the back yard.  Three main level bedrooms, including a primary bedroom with en-suite bathroom and two closets.  Or make one an office, there are two more bedrooms downstairs, one is huge with a full egress window. Great room area for your hobby, workout area, or just more space! Central air conditioning, a two car garage and more.  The best deal in Wiggins right now, make it yours!
